Output assets/cli-demo.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Padding 15
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "export BUDI_HOME=/tmp/budi-demo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "budi stats --period all"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "budi cost --period all"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "budi sessions --period week"
Enter
Sleep 4s
